title: I’m Not a Magical Girl - Novel Updates
tags: Hiding True Identity   Magical Girls   Male to Female   Monsters
author: Chi Tu De Shu Yu   吃土的书语
description: Why are others' powers so cool, but must I turn into a loli-magical girl to fight? Why do others' leave after fighting a monster in a cool way, but I must think of a way to escape those brainless fan's blockade? Why did I become more poor after becoming a super hero!? I'm done with this magical girl BS!>
